map "https://fhir.dk.swisstph-mis.ch/matchbox/fhir/StructureMap/emcare.b22.bronchodilatortest" = "emcare.b22.bronchodilatortest"


uses "http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/sdc/StructureDefinition/sdc-questionnaireresponse" alias 'questionnaireResponse' as source

uses "https://fhir.dk.swisstph-mis.ch/matchbox/fhir/StructureDefinition/observation" alias 'Observation' as target

group bundletrans(source src : questionnaireResponse, target bundle : Bundle) {
  src -> bundle.id = uuid() "id";
  src -> bundle.type = 'batch' "type";
  src where src.item.where(linkId = 'EmCare.B22.DE17').exists() then {
    src ->  bundle.entry as entry,  entry.request as request,  request.method = 'POST',  entry.resource = create('Observation') as tgt then emcareobservationemcareb22de17(src, tgt) "DE17";
  } "emcareobservation";
  src where src.item.where(linkId = 'EmCare.B22.DE18').exists() then {
    src ->  bundle.entry as entry,  entry.request as request,  request.method = 'POST',  entry.resource = create('Observation') as tgt then emcareobservationemcareb22de18(src, tgt) "DE18";
  } "emcareobservation";
  src where src.item.where(linkId = 'EmCare.B22.DE19').exists() then {
    src ->  bundle.entry as entry,  entry.request as request,  request.method = 'POST',  entry.resource = create('Observation') as tgt then emcareobservationemcareb22de19(src, tgt) "DE19";
  } "emcareobservation";
  src where src.item.where(linkId = 'EmCare.B22.DE20').exists() then {
    src ->  bundle.entry as entry,  entry.request as request,  request.method = 'POST',  entry.resource = create('Observation') as tgt then emcareobservationemcareb22de20(src, tgt) "DE20";
  } "emcareobservation";
  src where src.item.where(linkId = 'EmCare.B22.DE21').exists() then {
    src ->  bundle.entry as entry,  entry.request as request,  request.method = 'POST',  entry.resource = create('Observation') as tgt then emcareobservationemcareb22de21(src, tgt) "DE21";
  } "emcareobservation";
}

group emcareobservationemcareb22de17(source src, target tgt) {
  src ->  tgt.identifier = create('Identifier') as CodeID,  CodeID.system = 'http://hl7.org/fhir/namingsystem-identifier-type',  CodeID.use = 'official',  CodeID.value = 'uuid',  CodeID.id = uuid() "id-emcareb22de17";
  src ->  tgt.encounter = src.encounter,  tgt.subject = src.subject,  tgt.meta = create('Meta') as newMeta,  newMeta.profile = 'https://fhir.dk.swisstph-mis.ch/matchbox/fhir/StructureDefinition/emcareobservation',  tgt.code = create('CodeableConcept') as concept,  concept.system = 'https://fhir.dk.swisstph-mis.ch/matchbox/fhir/CodeSystem/emcare-custom-codes',  concept.code = 'EmCare.B22.DE17' "code-emcareb22de17";
  src.item as item where linkId = 'timestamp', item.answer as a -> tgt.issued = a "timestamp-emcareb22de17";
  src -> tgt.subject = src.subject "patient";
  src.item first as item where linkId = 'EmCare.B22.DE17' then {
    item.answer first as a then {
      a ->  tgt.value = a,  tgt.status = 'final' "val-emcareb22de17";
    } "an-emcareb22de17";
  } "it-emcareb22de17";
}
